---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	* Web Traffic Load Balancer

	* Same as LB but additional features

		* Autoscaling
		* URL based routing
		* Custom error pages
		* Header and URL rewrite
		* WAF (Web Application Firewall) - Protects apps from attacks 
		* SSL termination
		* Zone redundancy
		* More

	* Has to be in it's own VNET and Subnet

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

5 Configurations

	1. Backend Pools
	2. HTTPS Settings
	3. Frontend IP configuration
	4. Listeners - Recieves on specific port and protocol
	5. Rules - To connect backend pools

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------